data.description: Beautiful 4 Bedroom / 2 1/2 Bath in Valley View School District. 2401 sqft of very well laid out living space with split floor plan. Some of the Highlights include: Wood Floors and Stain Floors, No Carpet. Hunter Douglas Plantation Shutters. Has a Storm Shelter in the Garage. Cook Stove, Fireplace & Water Heater are all Natural Gas. Screen in Porch, Large Wooden Deck in the Back overlooking the Fenced Backyard. Fall is here, the backyard backs up to all the fall colors. All this setting on .22 +/- acre lot conveniently located near many of your local amenities and HWY 49 S. Call Today to Setup a Time to View This Amazing Property.
